Figures for the first half of 1992 were Pounds 1.36m (Pounds 1.05m) on
turnover static at Pounds 66.7m (Pounds 66.8m).
Basic earnings per share rose 18 per cent to 3.3p (2.8p) or 3.2p (2.7p)
fully diluted. The interim dividend is being maintained at 1.8p.
